import React from 'react'; import roadmap1 from '../images/roadmap1.png'; import roadmap2 from '../images/roadmap2.png'; import roadmap3 from '../images/roadmap3.png'; import roadmap4 from '../images/roadmap4.png'; import roadmap5 from '../images/roadmap5.svg'; import roadmap6 from '../images/roadmap6.png'; const Roadmap = () => { return (

) } export default Roadmap;
